  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, controlled trial evaluating the effect of an intraoperative infusion of
      intravenous ketamine and lidocaine on the quantity of opioid consumed postoperatively in
      cardiac surgery patients receiving a median sternotomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
